@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
autonumber

actor "Weather Person" as WeatherPerson
participant ":System" as System

activate WeatherPerson

WeatherPerson -> System : Requests to import bulk weather data

activate System
System --> WeatherPerson : Requests weather data source and file
deactivate System

WeatherPerson -> System : Provides source type and file

activate System
System --> System : Check if Weather Person is authorized
System --> System : Validate file format
System --> System : Read weather records
System --> System : Validate each weather record
System --> System : Check referenced air control areas

alt file is valid and contains valid records
    System --> System : Import valid weather records
    System --> WeatherPerson : Display import summary
else file is invalid
    System --> WeatherPerson : Display file format error message
else some records are invalid
    System --> System : Import valid records
    System --> WeatherPerson : Display partial import summary and validation errors
end

deactivate System
deactivate WeatherPerson

@enduml